{"tid":2318941,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警司陳凱港疑違法賣無註冊藥膏 藥劑師指敏感反應可致窒息","createTime":"2020-12-09T17:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T01:08:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":32,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0140fa89b93c5c0f787905b28a8053cadd52d377","tid":2318941,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:12:20.000Z","msg":"「警隊KOL」之一、人稱「海港Sir」的陳凱港，自「反送中運動」起因頻頻在網上發文而迅速冒起，不時借機宣傳其商城「小王子」品牌和「王子商城」。《蘋果》發現，「小王子」售賣的一款皮膚抑菌膏含氯己定成份，疑須於衞生署註冊為藥劑製品；衞生署回應查詢時確認有關產品未有註冊，根據相關條例，銷售未經註冊的藥劑製品最高可判罰款10萬元及監禁2年。警方稱不評論個別個案；又指非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，定必嚴正處理。陳凱港至截稿前未有回應，但發文暗批有人抓住瑕疵向其工作單位投訴舉報。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》發現，人稱「海港Sir」的沙田警區助理指揮官陳凱港有份投資的「小王子」和「王子商城」，一直售賣含氯己定成份、但未向當局註冊的藥膏。根據《藥劑業及毒藥條例》，銷售及管有未經註冊的藥劑製品屬刑事罪行，每項罪行最高可被判罰款10萬元及監禁兩年。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者早前到「小王子」位於藍田商場臨時展銷場視察，發現場內展示多款「西施蘭」品牌的貨品，但未見「西施蘭百消膏」。記者向店員查詢有否出售「皮膚病藥膏」後，店員即從枱底拿出數枝「西施蘭百消膏」，每枝售價26元，且「買4送1」，店員向記者推銷稱：「我依度都唔係剩番好多，頭先有個人都買咗一打走。」<br />\n<br />\n「小王子」除了在實體展銷場銷售氯己定藥膏外，亦有在其網上商店「王子商城」出售藥膏，售價相若；惟記者向查衞生署查詢後，相關藥膏已下架。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201210/3TVDXHJEKRBQHILKEXS3C4RRZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201210%2F3TVDXHJEKRBQHILKEXS3C4RRZU%2F&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUOaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=42789eb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201210%2F3TVDXHJEKRBQHILKEXS3C4RRZU%2F&h=697efa18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201210/3TVDXHJEKRBQHILKEXS3C4RRZU/</a>"},{"pid":"afbc744edeeca36b67e28b44604a34d9b21e6974","tid":2318941,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:13:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb43e6267325b6f24d6a60888fdff290a75a19d2","tid":2318941,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4c14f68508e68507a599d00e346cccec9eb50d","tid":2318941,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb43e6267325b6f24d6a60888fdff290a75a19d2","tid":2318941,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a893785e2142ffdacb3a9f14563ce9385622cbe2","tid":2318941,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac4c14f68508e68507a599d00e346cccec9eb50d","tid":2318941,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb43e6267325b6f24d6a60888fdff290a75a19d2","tid":2318941,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88e5f691c102e5bbe86f85147faa0cdd4eca557","tid":2318941,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be0447f659ec299d1a904f89fcf91c0b67ec58bc","tid":2318941,"uid":92448,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:16:22.000Z","msg":"黑警+狗官+太監=港共曱甴集團"},{"pid":"aa3881d78a7e73d84815e6e6a2f33b2df3d511e7","tid":2318941,"uid":134323,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:16:31.000Z","msg":"而家公務員可以光明正大秘撈？"},{"pid":"627c74b97b063aa527acfd3185db41eb403414f5","tid":2318941,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233f7fa7cf0ebbba0083f714e04c8556e1916076","tid":2318941,"uid":52271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:18:30.000Z","msg":"邊個敢拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5610454cdd4a86bd40d9511e40d40d377e46bd","tid":2318941,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"be0447f659ec299d1a904f89fcf91c0b67ec58bc","tid":2318941,"uid":92448,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:16:22.000Z","msg":"黑警+狗官+太監=港共曱甴集團"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b14a6a26dbf963d56b2e20ce3fce7886cbc27d","tid":2318941,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa3881d78a7e73d84815e6e6a2f33b2df3d511e7","tid":2318941,"uid":134323,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:16:31.000Z","msg":"而家公務員可以光明正大秘撈？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:20:24.000Z","msg":"根據警方公開的警察通例，警務人員必須事先獲得批核當局批准，才可以個人名義擔任外間工作，賺取任何酬勞，或接受任何的受薪職位。惟若警務人員並無接受任何金錢或物質的報酬，有關活動又被視為與《公務員事務規例》的原則無實際或可能出現的牴觸，則無須獲得當局批准。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警方對總警司或以上的首長級職位人員方有較嚴格的申報投資要求，警務人員一般無須申報其私人投資。而若警務人員供作慈善的投資，而且並無受益人的權益，更不視為《警察通例》下的「投資」。"},{"pid":"83234f992c94a9a1af9e25a5905a1091c9e2d8ce","tid":2318941,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:21:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">《蘋果》曾向陳凱港查詢，至截稿前未有回覆。但在《蘋果》向警方查詢當晚，陳則在其社交平台發文，批評有人抓住「既定目標」的每一個瑕疵，向其工作單位、管理部門等每一個可以投訴的地方投訴舉報，「給『既定目標』造成工作上的困擾和麻煩。甚至要面對那些人的投訴舉報所带来（帶來）的反反複復（覆覆）的調查詢問。」<br />\n<br />\n據報道，陳凱港於1979年來港，畢業於皇仁書院，1995年加入皇家香港警察，曾任紅磡分區總督察、財務部物料統籌科警司、新界南總區交通部警司，現為沙田警區助理指揮官，並於「中大保衞戰」期間，護送中國大陸學生離開中大。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"836463f039785d1f5fdc325a82b1f9249ee12db1","tid":2318941,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:32:46.000Z","msg":"黑警=知法犯法"},{"pid":"0f95ce44a7f1d930cc4d236c198b8ae255300195","tid":2318941,"uid":244034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GuvSgBG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGuvSgBG.jpg&h=1c3d4633&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47bfb7d9ea3c78af238d08546d137997ae380a0b","tid":2318941,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:42:16.000Z","msg":"賣冰都唔會有人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dea8d3f5c4dc978fc986d216db18e39de48b1de","tid":2318941,"uid":7854,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:43:44.000Z","msg":"犯法就係犯法<br />\n<br />\n除非你係香港曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd81615dbe6c8f4d0e7bee2886c74067e217dd6","tid":2318941,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:44:51.000Z","msg":"好快就會係反送中問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />